{"tid":788762,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［年經］點解香港可以做到全囡有仔","createTime":"2018-08-21T17:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T13:10:12.000Z","uid":67302,"like":15,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2ff976efaf02869c57d081a5c941ff22d62a9256","tid":788762,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:18:41.000Z","msg":"痴線 有時出街返工返學又好 見到條女試正少少<br />\n都心諗算鳩數一定有仔<br />\n咁諗住貪過癮問啲個樣無咁靚啲囡囡啦<br />\n都有仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好癲 人地有圖有真相（樣衰果啲無特別check）<br />\n但仔呢 有一半都無囡<br />\n點解個天要咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要個個大時大節 今年連鬼節都要提「單身狗過鬼節」呢類說話<br />\n好似單身係我錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左試圖搶女友係咪無辦法架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下世要做女人 坐享其成在香港過easy mode 人生"},{"pid":"dc4c7c979d0752f551836da346ae0e87ba90168f","tid":788762,"uid":202092,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:20:52.000Z","msg":"我明呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee2e23a82288568a540c11f2fb1be8ea452dd62","tid":788762,"uid":115441,"like":6,"dislike":43,"score":-37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"香港好似不嬲男多女少<br />\n唔洗咁灰wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a267a94ca3c0408104b774003f4153b2367fa45","tid":788762,"uid":4672,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:28:13.000Z","msg":"全部都係雞 你帽我 我帽你<br />\n<br />\n全港男人堪兄弟"},{"pid":"ee7b935e0b8f9b002ca1a5e61eb9773bec80008e","tid":788762,"uid":9315,"like":25,"dislike":5,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"bee2e23a82288568a540c11f2fb1be8ea452dd62","tid":788762,"uid":115441,"like":6,"dislike":43,"score":-37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:23:10.000Z","msg":"香港好似不嬲男多女少<br />\n唔洗咁灰wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"調轉